name: Fun Excavation Dig it Out Kit - Glow in the Dark Dinosaur
description:
Fun Excavation Dig it Out Kit - Glow in the Dark Dinosaur

Dig it out kits are a great way for kids to learn while having fun and making a mess. Each kit comes with everything you need to find the treasure inside. .

The block is made from gypsum and plaster so is safe for kids to dig in and the brush and tool are made from wood.

name: Fantasy Backflow Incense Burner - Magic Tree
description:
Fantasy Backflow Incense Burner - Magic Tree

Our range of backflow burners are made from resin and are for use with backflow incense cones only.

Backflow incense creates a mist when it is lit which flows down and around the backflow burner. This mist contains natural resins and oils that can create a light residue on the burner and surface around it which can be wiped clean with a damp cloth.

This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

Our backflow burners are a great focal point in any room and are the perfect gift for any fantasy or gothic collector.

This item comes with 1 backflow incense cone included.

name: Fantasy LED Backflow Incense Burner - Purple Dragon
description:

Our range of backflow burners are made from resin and are for use with backflow incense cones only.

Backflow incense creates a mist when it is lit which flows down and around the backflow burner. This mist contains natural resins and oils that can create a light residue on the burner and surface around it which can be wiped clean with a damp cloth.

This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

Our backflow burners are a great focal point in any room and are the perfect gift for any fantasy or gothic collector.

This item comes with 1 backflow incense cone included and required 2 AA batteries which are not included.

name: Backflow Incense Burner - Dragons Head
description:
Backflow Incense Burner - Dragons Head

Our range of backflow burners are made from resin and are for use with backflow incense cones only.

Backflow incense creates a mist when it is lit which flows down and around the backflow burner. This mist contains natural resins and oils that can create a light residue on the burner and surface around it which can be wiped clean with a damp cloth.

This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

Our backflow burners are a great focal point in any room and are the perfect gift for any fantasy or gothic collector.

This item comes with 1 backflow incense cone included and a small foam mat to help protect the heatproof surface the burner is placed on.

name: Spirit Wolf Protector of the North Tiered Trinket Display Stand
description:
Spirit Wolf Protector of the North Tiered Trinket Display Stand

Mini collectable and trinket display stands are a great displaying all your favourite items. There are loads of themes to choose from so we know you will find one just for you.

Made from resin they are strong and durable and will look great with all your treasures displayed on the different layers and levels. The resin is suitable for outdoors but if left in an exposed location the paint finish may start to weather.
